*Glavni* grad Srbije je Beograd. (The main capital of Serbia is Belgrade.)

*Glavnim* ciljem je da ostvari zadatu zadaću. (The main goal is to accomplish the assigned task.)

On je *glavni* krivac za nastalu situaciju. (He is the main culprit for the situation that arose.)

Kompanija je poznata po *glavnim* proizvodima. (The company is known for its main products.)

Ona je *glavna* učesnica u ovom projektu. (She is the main participant in this project.)